claim: For patients examined in the laboratory in October 1991, the average age as of 1999 was below 40 years.
extra_info: average age of patients as of year 1999 refers to AVG(SUBTRACT('1999', year(Birthday))); October of 1991 refers to Date BETWEEN '1991-10-01' AND '1991-10-30'
reasoning: The average age as of 1999 for patients examined in the laboratory in October 1991 is approximately 47.65 (counting all lab rows) or 48.31 (counting distinct patients). Both values are well above 40, contradicting the claim that the average age was below 40 years.

content.text: Now let me query for patients examined in the Laboratory in October 1991 and compute their average age as of 1999.

input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/thrombosis_prediction.sqlite" "SELECT AVG(1999 - CAST(strftime('%Y', P.Birthday) AS INT)) AS avg_age FROM Laboratory L JOIN Patient P ON L.ID = P.ID WHERE L.Date BETWEEN '1991-10-01' AND '1991-10-30';"
input.description: Calculate average age as of 1999 for patients with lab exams in October 1991

input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/thrombosis_prediction.sqlite" "SELECT P.ID, P.Birthday, L.Date, 1999 - CAST(strftime('%Y', P.Birthday) AS INT) AS age_1999 FROM Laboratory L JOIN Patient P ON L.ID = P.ID WHERE L.Date BETWEEN '1991-10-01' AND '1991-10-30';"
input.description: List individual patients and their ages for verification

content.text: The average across all rows is ~47.65, but some patients have multiple lab entries. Let me also check with distinct patients to be thorough:

input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claimdb/test_dbs/thrombosis_prediction.sqlite" "SELECT AVG(1999 - CAST(strftime('%Y', P.Birthday) AS INT)) AS avg_age FROM (SELECT DISTINCT L.ID FROM Laboratory L WHERE L.Date BETWEEN '1991-10-01' AND '1991-10-30') D JOIN Patient P ON D.ID = P.ID;"
input.description: Average age using distinct patients only

content.text:
Whether we count each row (47.65) or each distinct patient (48.31), the average age as of 1999 is well above 40 years, not below 40 as the claim asserts.
